00:00:30.569 --> 00:00:33.790
 ... who were sacrificed in ritual ceremonies. 

00:00:33.790 --> 00:00:39.120
 Unbar performs these rituals to honor the unfinished land ghosts. 

00:00:39.120 --> 00:00:45.215
 Blurred realities that only the most knowledgeable witch doctors can see. 

00:00:45.671 --> 00:00:51.886
 Recently, one of these warriors defied his spiritual leaders, ... 

00:00:52.060 --> 00:00:55.410
 ... in the belief that they were corrupt. 

00:00:55.410 --> 00:01:01.425
 Despite being deported for his position, this witch doctor is relentless ... 

00:01:01.570 --> 00:01:11.283
 ... and set out on the path of faith and honor that will bring him in the face of the demonic forces threatening the world of Sanctuary. 

00:01:13.783 --> 00:01:20.048
 Witch doctor has superhuman abilities that destroy the enemy's mind and body ... 

00:01:20.083 --> 00:01:24.740
 ... with dangerous diseases, alchemy, and ancient rites. 

00:01:24.740 --> 00:01:32.927
 The use of these abilities is made up of mana, a mystic energy that slowly complements. 

00:01:33.130 --> 00:01:40.753
 In order to increase the amount of mana, he can put on a terrible tribal equipment charged with magic. 

00:01:40.970 --> 00:01:48.036
 This allows him to cast almost unlimited spells and incantations against his enemies. 

00:01:51.520 --> 00:01:55.290
 Although he can directly injure his opponents, ... 

00:01:55.290 --> 00:01:59.439
 ... some of his skills are much more insidious. 

00:01:59.570 --> 00:02:04.510
 For example, Horrify scares the closest enemy ... 

00:02:04.510 --> 00:02:09.369
 ... while Mass Confusion cancels the border between friend and enemy ... 

00:02:09.404 --> 00:02:12.783
 ... and turn even the most loyal comrades into the enemy's life and death. 

00:02:12.979 --> 00:02:20.359
 Yet these curses are nothing against the ability to induce ugly monsters from the underworld. 

00:02:21.089 --> 00:02:27.006
 Using their mana stores can easily flood the earth with poisonous frogs. 

00:02:27.331 --> 00:02:31.317
 Order cruel monsters to tear their enemies ... 

00:02:31.701 --> 00:02:36.400
 ... and launch a flock of fire bats to light their opponents. 

00:02:36.400 --> 00:02:40.189
 But the most frightening of all is Gargantuan, ... 

00:02:40.454 --> 00:02:46.258
 ... a huge, ugly creature that can easily cope with any demon. 

00:02:48.699 --> 00:02:54.699
 Witch doctor is a fearless warrior who doesn't give the enemy any chance. 

00:02:54.699 --> 00:02:59.239
 But he also longs for the knowledge and secrets of the world. 

00:02:59.389 --> 00:03:08.235
 His mission to fight the demons to the ghost's glory is noble and will not end until it is over. 

00:03:08.419 --> 00:03:15.708
